      <title>欧洲央行行长斯托纳拉斯敦促关注气候变化对经济的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-10/central-banks-urged-to-consider-climate-change-impact-on-inflation-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员雅尼斯·斯图尔纳拉斯在卡西梅里尼写道，欧洲央行将利用新的权力，试图减少发行资产的实体的碳排放，并补充说，气候变化的影响将影响通胀和增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-10/central-banks-urged-to-consider-climate-change-impact-on-inflation-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 10:29:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
