    <item>
      <title>由于选民投票，埃及通胀连续第二个月放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-10/egypt-inflation-slows-offering-sisi-boost-as-voters-head-to-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及通胀连续第二个月放缓，达到五月份以来的最低水平，在总统选举投票开始之际给当局带来了一定程度的好消息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-10/egypt-inflation-slows-offering-sisi-boost-as-voters-head-to-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 06:44:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
